                        "description": "",
                        "id": "",
                        "params": {
                            "fontSize": 12,
                            "markdown": "**Overview**\n\nThis dashboard provides a clear view of Adapter events collected from Axonius.\n\nIt includes a Pie chart for Adapter by Status, providing a quick breakdown of adapter availability and health. A saved search highlights Adapter Essential Details, giving immediate visibility into key adapter attributes. A stacked bar chart for Connection Status Per Adapter shows the distribution of active, inactive, warning, and error connections across each adapter. Another saved search lists Connections With Errors, helping teams quickly identify and troubleshoot problematic integrations.\n\n**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/axonius)**\n",
